1. Sude mi za prekršaj. (*sude*) (They are judging me for a misdemeanor.) 
2. Oni suđe o tome odlučiće sutra. (*suđe*) (They will decide about it tomorrow in court.)
3. Sudjelujem u humanitarnoj akciji. (*sudjelujem*) (I am participating in a humanitarian action.)
4. *Sudim* da ćeš se svidjeti mom bratu. (*Sudim*) (I judge that you will be liked by my brother.)
5. Oni sude pravedno. (*sude*) (They judge fairly.)
6. Mogu li ti *suditi* po izgledu da si sretan? (*suditi*) (Can I judge by your appearance that you are happy?)
7. Koliko će trajati suđenje? (*suđenje*) (How long will the trial last?)
8. Zanimljivo mi je *suditi* knjige prema omotu. (*suditi*) (I find it interesting to judge books by their covers.) 
9. Njih dvoje se *sude* na sudu. (*sude*) (Those two are being sued in court.)
10. Ona se ne voli *suditi* sa drugima. (*suditi*) (She doesn't like to judge others.)